IMAPAccount personal
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
Host imap.gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg --quiet --for-your-eyes-only --decrypt ~/.password-store/gmail/mbsync.gpg | head -1"
PipelineDepth 50
SSLType IMAPS
Timeout 60
User torsneyt@gmail.com

IMAPStore personal-remote
Account personal

MaildirStore personal-local
Flatten .
Inbox /home/tom/.mail/personal/INBOX
Path /home/tom/.mail/personal/
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel personal
Create Both
Expunge Both
Master :personal-remote:
Patterns * INBOX ![Gmail]/* !sent !archive !spam !trash
Remove Both
Slave :personal-local:
SyncState *


