Create Both
Expunge Both
Master :univie-remote:
Patterns * INBOX !Archive !Sent !Trash !Junk !Drafts !archive !sent !trash !spam !drafts
Remove Both
Slave :univie-local:
SyncState *


IMAPAccount work
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
Host outlook.office365.com
PassCmd "gpg --quiet --for-your-eyes-only --decrypt ~/.password-store/swansea.ac.uk.gpg | head -1"
