Patterns * !Calendar* !Contacts "!Conversation History*" !Journal !Notes !Tasks "!RSS Subscriptions*" !Outbox "!Sync Issues*" !students !Archive "!Sent Items" "!Deleted Items" "!Junk Email" !Drafts !archive !sent !trash !spam !drafts
Remove Both
Slave :work-local:
SyncState *



